# Backend Engineer - Nodejs, Typescript 

**Backend Engineer (Node.js/TypeScript)**

Location: Paris (Remote friendly, 1 day per week at the office)

** About the Role **

We are seeking an experienced Backend Engineer with over 3 years of experience in Node.js and TypeScript to join our dynamic team at StaffMe. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in testing and scalable environments, with additional experience in Angular being a plus. This role requires proficiency in English and a keen ability to collaborate in an international setting.

** Key Responsibilities **

Develop and maintain backend services using Node.js and TypeScript.
Ensure code quality through rigorous testing and best practices.
Collaborate with front-end developers to integrate user-facing elements with server-side logic.
Optimize applications for maximum speed and scalability.
Manage database systems (mySQL) and messaging queues (RabbitMQ).

** Qualifications **

Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Computer Science.
3+ years of experience with Node.js and TypeScript.
Experience with Angular is a plus.
Strong experience in testing and scalable environments.
Proficient in English.
Our Tech Stack:

Front-end: Ionic/Angular/TypeScript (iOS, Android, Web)
Back-end: TypeScript/Node.js/mySQL/RabbitMQ

** Benefits **

Competitive salary up to 60k
Comprehensive insurance
Opportunity to work in an international environment (Europe)
Meal tickets
Team buildings & much more
